WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.523
Strong video updates follow a recipe. Practice it once before you record —

00:00:03.573 --> 00:00:07.095
you will sound prepared, not rehearsed. Open with the customer's name and your

00:00:07.145 --> 00:00:10.668
name. Identify the vehicle and the service. Then point the camera at what

00:00:10.718 --> 00:00:14.240
you are explaining — let them see the worn part, the leak, the

00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:17.813
measurement. And always close with a clear next step. I will call you

00:00:17.863 --> 00:00:21.385
this afternoon at three is a next step. Call us back is not.

00:00:21.435 --> 00:00:24.958
Give them something to do.
